Package edu.byu.ece.rapidSmith.bitstreamTools.configurationSpecification

Interface XilinxConfigurationSpecification

All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractConfigurationSpecification, V4ConfigurationSpecification, V56ConfigurationSpecification, V5ConfigurationSpecification, V6ConfigurationSpecification
public interface XilinxConfigurationSpecification
Specifies the parameters for the configuration data associated with a Xilinx FPGA. This interface is independent of the family and the part. Classes that implement this interface provide all the appropriate parameter data for querying the configuration bitstream.
Author:
wirthlin
